snippet.title: rIVerseLive
snippet.description:
Hello!

We are rIVerse, a Toronto-based pop/r&b group with a mission to represent the underrepresented. 

The rIVerseLive channel is home to our popular reaction series, 'rIVerse Reacts.' As artists who create pop music ourselves, rIVerse offers a unique perspective on all elements of mainstream releases - songwriting, music production, styling and choreography to name a few.

The series is also known and trusted for our #HonesTEA; we always share our honest opinions and you can know that when rIVerse says we like something, we truly mean it.

This series takes the very popular 'reaction video' concept on YouTube and elevates it to a full-production entertainment program.

Thank you for visiting the rIVerseLive YouTube channel and we hope you will subscribe to join The IV League!

*****

Interested in sending fan mail, gifts, products, etc.? Feel free to mail to:

rIVerse
PO Box 60013 Queen Beverley PO
Toronto, ON
M5V 0C5
